      "title": "Fuel tankers are rushing in",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation has informed that three diesel vessels and one petrol vessel will visit the country on the 17th.",
        "Three diesel vessels of 40,000 MT each and one octane 92 petrol vessel of 35,000 MT will arrive in the country."
      ],
